headlines.description: — O.G. Anunoby scored 12 of his 26 points in the fourth quarter, Fred VanVleet also had 26, and the Toronto Raptors beat Dallas 105-100 Saturday, snapping a four-game losing streak against the Mavericks.
headlines.shortLinkText: Anunoby scores 12 of his 26 in 4th, Raptors top Mavs 105-100

events.name: Oklahoma City Thunder at Houston Rockets

headlines.description: — Jalen Green had 28 points and a career-high nine assists, Alperen Sengun added 21 points, a career-best 18 rebounds and seven assists, and the Houston Rockets beat the Oklahoma City Thunder 118-105 on Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Green, Sengun, Smith lead Rockets past Thunder, 118-105

events.name: Los Angeles Lakers at San Antonio Spurs

headlines.description: — LeBron James picked the perfect time for his best offensive output of the season.
headlines.shortLinkText: James' season-high 39 points lead Lakers by Spurs, 143-138

headlines.description: — There was much debate during the NBA offseason about whether Deandre Ayton was worth a max contract.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ayton has 29 points, 21 rebounds as Suns edge Jazz 113-112
